This is xmppbot, an xmpp or jabber bot written in C++ using gloox and boost.

=Dependecies=
- Boost 1.4.x ( tested with 1.4.7.0 and 1.4.8.0 )
- Gloox 1.0
- sqlite3 ( optional )
- soci ( optional )

=Building=
Either use the supplied Code::Blocks project file or the included Makefile

=Configuration=

Either create a copy of the example config-file in the bin/ subfolder and adapt it to suit your needs and start the bot with "/path/to/bot/xmppbot myconfig.cfg" or use the create_basic_config.sh to create a sqlite config( which the bot uses as default )..
The configuration options are documented in the example config file.
